query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-listfragment',
'basic-authentication',
'currency',
'docx',
'expression-blend',
'jython',
'kendo-asp.net-mvc',
'loading',
'monodevelop',
'mysql-connector',
'nhibernate-mapping',
'pillow',
'remote-access',
'restlet');
